<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Distress Call</title>

    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
      }

      div {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 2px solid #ff5050;
        border-radius: 10px;
        background-color: #660000;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 80, 80, 0.5);
      }

      h1 {
        color: #ff5050;
        font-size: 2em;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: white;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div>
      <h1>Distress Call</h1>
      <p>
        <strong>Emergency! SOS!</strong><br />
        This is a distress call. We require immediate assistance. Our
        coordinates are [Your Coordinates]. Please respond urgently. Time is of
        the essence.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
